If wisps are the same everywhere, then I don't think there's any faction with them.  I've been killing hosts of the wind, wisps, ghost lights etc. in Midgard and no faction hits.  Pretty nice, those guys are neutral so I can hunt in areas where they spawn and not worry when I'm resting up that anything's going to jump me.<br>
