<br>
If I were a white guy, and I knew you killed 2 white guys, I'd want you dead as well.<br>
<br>
(if that sounds incredibly stupid and borderline-racist, good - it's supposed to - this is what the above quote sounds like taken out of a fantasy context)<br>
<br>
Seriously, the idea of this racial fanaticism is taken to ridiculous extremes in most RPGs. It's a fault of the genre as a whole, not just DAoC. Take, for example, EQ's pigeonholing of dark elves -- they HAVE to be evil. Essentially what this says is that the race as a whole is even more like-minded than, say, dogs - creatures who's behavior is characterized by their breed (even dogs, however, have large variations in personality within the same breed). So, essentially, dark elves are so exceedingly simplistic (the implications of such: stupidity, self-righteousness, etc. I won't get in to), that even dogs display a more complex personality schema. <br>
<br>
And it doesn't stop there -- it's very common for a race to not only have their society and world views nailed down as being completely uniform, but often their personal choices are, too. For instance, if a dwarf wanted to worship, say, Prexus, why the hell not?<br>
<br>
*sigh* I'm getting way off-topic. Suffice it to say that the idea of basing a faction on a race is extremely stupid. That being said, I also vote for those damned leprechauns -- unless you feel like being harassed everywhere you go, leave them alone... or do what I do, and make a macro that says &quot;Gimme your damned Lucky Charms&quot; and then proceed to spam it while you beat down every worthless leprechaun in sight.   ;) <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udragoon412.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dragoon412</A> at: 12/22/01 9:47:23 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ucloudien.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cloudien</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(3/5/02 11:57:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=200.topic&index=25>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.cloudk.clara.net/storage/zidane2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re:  Monsters you wished you stayed friends with.</span><hr size=1> Seems impossible to keep the leprechaun faction up... destroyed mine yesterday <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
